snippet.textDisplay:
Doing this dance is like doing pilates, looks simple but actually using the core muscles that you never know it exists, to perfect that movements as simple as lifting the leg looking gracefully yet full of power from the muscles. They have always been incorporating new learned dance moves with their own BTS style which is - fast powerful with slow steady moves, playing with heights by moving up and down, and playing with images of circles and spread in/out like a flower blooming. BTS dance genre can only be summarized as one genre which is BTS.

P/s and what i love about their choreo is, nobody is trying hard trying to outshine the others. There is no "i dance better" vibe as always, whether you are start out as good dancer or not, when it comes to BTS teamwork is first. Maybe thats why they are so loved
